\c 19
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika pakunzwa kwamambo Hezekia, kuti wakabvarura nguvo dzake\x + 18.37.\x*, ndokuzvifukidza saga\x + 1 Madz. 20.31.\x*, ndokupinda muimba yaJehovha\x + 19.14. Map. 73.16,17. 1 Madz. 8.29,30.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino wakatuma Eriakimu waiva pamusoro peimba, naShebhina munyori, nevakuru vevapristi, vakazvifukidza masaga\x + 1 Madz. 20.31.\x* kuna Isaya muporofita mwanakomana waAmozi\x + 2 Makor. 32.20.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino vakati kwaari: Anoreva seizvi Hezekia: Zuva rino izuva redambudziko nerekusvorwa nekunyomba, nokuti vana vakasvika pakuzvarwa, asi kusina simba rekuzvara.
\v 4 Zvimwe Jehovha Mwari wako achanzwa mashoko ese aRabhi-Shake\x + 2 Sam. 16.12.\x*, mambo weAsiriya tenzi wake waakatuma kuzvidza Mwari mupenyu\x + 19.16. 18.35. 1 Sam. 17.26.\x*, nekumhura pamashoko Jehovha\x + Map. 50.21.\x* Mwari wako aakanzwa\x + Num.. 12.2. 1 Sam. 7.9.\x*; naizvozvo simudzirai vakasara vanowanikwa munyengetero\x + 17.6. Isa. 1.9.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino varanda vamambo Hezekia vakasvika kuna Isaya.
\v 6 Isaya ndokuti kwavari: Muchareva seizvi kuna tenzi wenyu: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Usatya nekuda kwemashoko awakanzwa, varanda vamambo weAsiriya avakandimhura nawo\x + 18.17,28. 2 Sam. 9.9.\x*.
\v 7 Tarira, ndichaisa\x + 19.35,36,37.\x* mweya maari\x + Jer. 51.1. Isa. 37.7.\x*, uye achanzwa runyerekupe, uye achadzokera kunyika yake; uye ndichamuwisisa nemunondo munyika yake\x + 19.9. 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Rabhi-Shake wakadzokera, ndokuwana mambo weAsiriya achirwa neRibhina\x + Josh. 10.29.\x*; nokuti waiva anzwa kuti wabva paRakishi\x + 18.14.\x*.
\v 9 Wakati achinzwa zvaTirihaka\x + 1 Sam. 23.27.\x* mambo weItiyopiya\x + Isa. 11.11. 18.1. 20.3-5. 43.3. 45.14. Gen.. 10.6.\x*, zvichinzi: Tarirai, wabuda kuzorwa newe, zvino wakatendeuka ndokutuma nhume kuna Hezekia, achiti:
\v 10 Uchataura seizvi kuna Hezekia mambo waJudha uchiti: Mwari wako waunovimba naye\x + 18.5.\x* ngaarege kukunyengera achiti: Jerusarema haringapiwi muruoko rwamambo weAsiriya\x + 18.29,30.\x*.
\v 11 Tarira, iwe wakanzwa madzimambo eAsiriya zvaakaitira kunyika dzese, kudziparadza; zvino iwe uchasunungurwa here?
\v 12 Vamwari vendudzi vakasunungura here avo madzibaba angu avakaparadza\x + 18.33.\x*: Gozani\x + 17.6.\x*, naHarani\x + Gen.. 11.31. 27.43.\x*\x + Eze. 27.23. Amo. 1.5.\x*, naRezefi, nevana vaEdheni\x + Eze. 27.23. Amo. 1.5.\x* vaiva paTerasari\x + Isa. 37.12.\x*?
\v 13 Aripi mambo weHamati\x + 18.34.\x*, namambo weAripadhi\x + Isa. 37.13.\x*, namambo weguta reSefarivhaimi, Hena, neIvha?
\p
\v 14 Zvino Hezekia wakagamuchira tsamba muruoko rwenhume, ndokudziverenga. Hezekia ndokukwira kuimba yaJehovha, ndokuiwaridza pamberi paJehovha\x + 19.9. 2 Makor. 32.17.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino Hezekia wakanyengetera pamberi paJehovha\x + 2 Makor. 32.20.\x* ndokuti: Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, agere \add pakati pe\add*makerubhi\x + Eki. 25.22.\x*! Imwi muri Mwari, imwi moga, weushe hwese hwenyika; imwi makaita matenga nenyika\x + 19.19. 1 Madz. 18.39. Neh. 9.6. Jer. 10.10,12. Map. 86.10.\x*.
\v 16 Jehovha, rerekerai nzeve yenyu mugonzwa\x + Map. 31.2. 71.2. Dhan. 9.18.\x*; vhurai meso enyu, Jehovha, muone\x + Dhan. 9.18. 2 Makor. 6.40.\x*, munzwe mashoko aSani-Heribhi, aakamutuma nawo kuzozvidza Mwari mupenyu\x + 19.4.\x*.
\v 17 Zvirokwazvo, Jehovha, madzimambo eAsiriya akaparadza ndudzi nenyika dzadzo,
\v 18 ndokukandira vamwari vadzo mumoto; nokuti vaiva vasiri vamwari, asi basa remaoko emunhu, danda neibwe; naizvozvo vakavaparadza\x + Map. 115.4. 2 Makor. 32.19.\x*.
\v 19 Naizvozvo zvino, Jehovha Mwari wedu, tiponesei henyu kubva paruoko rwake, kuti ushe hwese hwenyika huzive kuti imwi muri Jehovha Mwari, imwi moga\x + Josh. 4.24.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Zvino Isaya mwanakomana waAmozi wakatuma kuna Hezekia achiti: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri: Zvawanyengetera kwandiri maererano naSani-Heribhi mambo weAsiriya ndakunzwa\x + 20.5.\x*.
\v 21 Iri ishoko Jehovha raataura maererano naye: Mhandara, mukunda weZiyoni, anokuzvidza, anokusveveredza\x + Marir. 2.13.\x*; mukunda weJerusarema wakadzungudza musoro shure kwako\x + Job. 16.4. Map. 22.7. 109.25. Marir. 2.15.\x*.
\v 22 Ndiani wawakatuka\x + 19.4.\x* nekunyomba\x + 19.6.\x*? Uye wakasimudzira ani inzwi, wakasimudzira meso ako kumusoro? Kurwisa Mutsvene waIsraeri\x + Map. 71.22. Isa. 5.24. 60.9. Jer. 51.5.\x*.
\v 23 Neruoko rwenhume dzako wakatuka Ishe\x + 18.17.\x*, ndokuti: Neuwandu hwedzingoro dzangu ini ndakakwira pakakwirira pemakomo\x + Map. 20.7.\x*, kumativi eRebhanoni\x + Jer. 22.6,23. Vato. 9.15.\x*. Zvino ndichatema misidhari yaro mirefu, miti yemisipiresi yakasarudzwa yaro\x + Jer. 22.6,23. Vato. 9.15.\x*, uye ndichapinda panzvimbo yekugara yemucheto wayo, sango raro dema\x + Josh. 19.26.\x*.
\v 24 Ini ndakachera ndikanwa mvura yeutorwa, uye nepasi petsoka dzangu ndakapwisa nzizi dzose dzenzvimbo dzakashoshewa.
\v 25 Hauna kunzwa here kuti ndakazviita kare\x + Isa. 45.7.\x*, panguva dzekare, kuti ndakazviumba? Ikozvino ndaita zviitike, kuti ungava wekuparadza maguta akashoshewa, ave matutu ematongo\x + Isa. 10.5.\x*.
\v 26 Naizvozvo vagari vawo vaiva neruoko rupfupi, vakatya, ndokunyara, vaiva \add se\add*uswa hwesango, nemuriwo munyoro\x + Gen.. 1.11.\x*, uswa hwedenga reimba, nezviyo zvakatsva zvisati zvakura\x + Map. 129.6.\x*.
\v 27 Asi ndinoziva kugara kwako, nekubuda kwako, nekupinda kwako, uye kunditsamwira kwako\x + 1 Sam. 29.6.\x*.
\v 28 Nekuda kwekunditsamwira kwako, uye kuti ruzha rwako rwakakwira munzeve dzangu, ndichaisa haka yangu mumhino dzako, netomu rangu mumiromo yako\x + Job. 41.2. Isa. 30.28. Eze. 29.4. 38.4. Amo. 4.2.\x*, ndikudzosere nenzira yawakauya nayo\x + 19.33,36.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Zvino ichi chichava chiratidzo kwauri\x + 20.8,9. 1 Sam. 2.34. Isa. 7.11,14. Ruk. 2.12. 1 Madz. 13.3.\x*: Uchadya gore rino zvinozvimerera\x + Rev. 25.5,11. Rev. 25.21,22.\x*, uye mugore rechipiri zvinotunga kubva pazviri; asi negore rechitatu dzvarai, mugokohwa, mudzvare minda yemizambiringa, mudye zvibereko zvayo.
\v 30 Zvino zvakapukunyuka zveimba yaJudha\x + 2 Makor. 32.22,23.\x* zvakasara zvichatsirazve midzi pasi, zvibereke zvibereko kumusoro.
\v 31 Nokuti muJerusarema muchabuda zvakasara, nezvakapukunyuka pagomo reZiyoni. Kushingaira kwaJehovha kuchaita izvi\x + Isa. 9.7.\x*.
\v 32 Naizvozvo anoreva seizvi Jehovha maererano namambo weAsiriya: Haangapindi muguta iri, kana kupfura musevemo, kana kuuya pamberi paro nenhovo, kana kututira gomo revhu pakatarisana naro\x + 2 Sam. 20.15.\x*.
\v 33 Nenzira yaakauya nayo, achadzokazve naiyoyo\x + 19.28.\x*, uye haangapindi muguta rino, anoreva Jehovha.
\v 34 Nokuti ndichadzivirira guta rino kuriponesa\x + 20.6. Isa. 31.5.\x* nekuda kwangu uye nekuda kwaDhavhidhi muranda wangu\x + 1 Madz. 11.13.\x*.
\v 35 Zvino zvakaitika usiku ihwohwo\x + 2 Makor. 32.21. Hos. 1.7.\x*, kuti mutumwa waJehovha wakabuda\x + 2 Sam. 24.16.\x* ndokurova pamusasa weVaAsiriya zvuru zana nemakumi masere nezvishanu; pavakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani, zvino tarira, vese vava zvitunha zvakafa\x + 19.8.\x*.
\v 36 Naizvozvo Sani-Heribhi mambo weAsiriya wakabva, ndokuenda, ndokudzokera, ndokugara muNinivhe\x + Gen.. 10.11. Jona 1.2.\x*.
\v 37 Zvino zvakaitika paaishumira muimba yaNisiroki mwari wake, Adhiramereki naSharezari\x + 17.31.\x* vanakomana vake vakamurova nemunondo, ivo ndokupukunyukira kunyika yeArarati\x + 19.7.\x*. Esari-Hadhoni mwanakomana wake ndokutonga pachinzvimbo chake\x + Ezi. 4.2.\x*.